HapPy Paint

Features

Required:

    1. Create a paint/sketch desktop application which allows the user to draw with a   mouse.
    2. Support multiple colors (minimum of 4 red green blue black)
    3. Implement an erase function to erase all or parts of the screen
    4. Implement a pen width function to adjust the pen width
    5. Document your code to the level of an intermediate developer reader
    6. Screen shot from each developer’s system
    7. Feedback showing which color is currently selected
    8. Resizable window

Additional features (+30pts)

    1. Implement basic fundamental geometric shapes (square, circle, triangle, etc.,)
    2. Implement a copy paste function that can copy a selection and paste it
    elsewhere on the screen
    3. Implement an undo function with memory of last 5 actions
    4. Implement “spray paint” or other interesting feature
    5. Implement a save and load feature to save your drawings
    6. Wild card – something you and your partner think is cool! (and you think I will
    also)

